# Bank Card Manager Application

![Swing GUI Application](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=Bank+Card+Manager+Screenshot)

A Java Swing application for managing bank card information with secure input validation and data management features.

## Features

- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Secure Input Validation**
  - 16-digit card numbers with auto-formatting
  - Full name validation for card holders
  - MM/YY expiry date format enforcement
  - 3-digit CVV verification
- ğŸ“‹ **Data Management**
  - Tabular display of stored cards
  - Safe deletion with confirmation dialog
  - Non-editable table protection
- ğŸ¯ **User-Friendly Interface**
  - Clear input form with real-time validation
  - Visual feedback for errors
  - Responsive table interactions

## System Requirements

- Java Runtime Environment (JRE) 8+
- 1024Ã—768 minimum display resolution

## Installation & Usage

### Quick Start
```bash
git clone [repository-url]
cd bank-card-manager
javac *.java
java BankCardManager
```

### Step-by-Step Guide
1. **Compilation**
   ```bash
   javac BankCardManager.java AddCardListener.java DeleteCardListener.java
   ```
2. **Execution**
   ```bash
   java BankCardManager
   ```

